{
  "texts": [
    "Some outputs included state law violations.",
    "Because this was contrary to the prompt's instructions, these were automatically considered as false positives for the sake of scoring.",
    "Figure 1 depicts our scoring process for the output for one run of our test case.",
    "After applying these rules manually to the output, we evaluate GPT-3.5's performance at this legal reasoning task.",
    "We used our previously defined, adapted concepts of true positives, false positives, and false negatives to calculate precision and recall (similarly to how Ting (2010) applied such metrics to a document retrieval system, as we were, essentially, asking GPT-3.5 to retrieve relevant laws from a finite set of laws)."
  ]
}